{"tid":1634413,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《難聽真話》唔該大家帶腦諗下勇武係咪真係要停，關人權法閪事咩","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T08:57:58.000Z","uid":161430,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9cde391151f6b41c6383f6886b73c7d8e1c3a8e8","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:51:33.000Z","msg":"首先，歡迎你地係咁負皮我，我會好開心，<br />\n因為將來大把屍比我鞭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返正題，我想講，繼<strong>「星期五警察少咗人係計」</strong><br />\n<strong>「林鄭就係想我地咁，唔好勇武喇」</strong>後，<br />\n最新叫停勇武講法又多咗樣，今次係：<br />\n<strong>「今晚勇武真係停 否則影響人權法」</strong><br />\n<strong>「所以等多一個禮拜先」#</strong>haha#dog<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該，你班人唔好咁撚蠢好冇</span>，<br />\n再講多次：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人權法通過與否，同勇武抗爭係完全冇關係。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個二個似乎唔記得，<span style=\"color: red;\">外國有人講過既係：<br />\n成立臨時政府會影響法案，但冇大力講係關勇武事。</span><br />\n<br />\n勇武唔停 = 人權法過唔倒 = 今晚開花唔好再爆，<br />\n係好突然出現既風聲，而，<br />\n18區開花明明喺星期五晚先極之成功。<br />\n只不過係幾日前既事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幾日前，大家其實甚至仲講緊：<br />\n「蒙面法一出 香港人就起義啦」「革命就會黎」</span><br />\n跟住又share梁天琦講蒙面法果張圖。<br />\n<br />\n結果呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">本來你地真係做倒，星期五令敵退</span>，<br />\n佢地人手唔夠，<span style=\"color: red;\">但你地事後竟然以為係個局。</span><br />\n<br />\n跟住，<span style=\"color: red;\">求撚其有班蛋散吹話勇武落去，<br />\n人權法就唔會過，你地竟然咁都信</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係mon po狗一定笑到仆街：<br />\n今晚勇武人少左，我班手足又可以輕鬆拉甲由又有ot錢。<br />\n<br />\n明明你地，已經捉到鹿，埋牙等贏，搵倒致命方法，<br />\n但你地呢一刻選擇放低隻鹿，話勇武要停，<br />\n唔好去脫角，因為咁係中計，影響人權法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係希望，你地唔好咁咁易受人擺佈。<br />\n<ins>更希望係你地智商可以高少少。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實，真正可以贏，就係保持開花，<br />\n和理非唔鐘意打，咁咪去貼連儂牆，<br />\n究竟勇武同和理非幾時又變成二元對立？<br />\n連最基本既各自努力原則，你都做唔返咩？<br />\n三日唔埋就喺度搵理由叫停勇武。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n至於勇武，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔裝修藍絲店？冇問題，<br />\n咁咪修黨鐵同政府合署囉，影響人權法條春咩？<br />\n跟住聽日咪三罷囉</span>，到聽日想唱歌咪唱飽佢。<br />\n<br />\n點解有人係都要話今晚唔好勇武呢？<br />\n點解格硬吹到今晚勇左會影響人權法呢？<br />\n點解早一兩日又話敵退走係計，唔好再勇武呢？<br />\n&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇留意，任何講法，講極，<br />\n都係離不開一樣宗旨呢，就係：<br />\n你停手，你乖乖地唱下歌先好。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢種msg邊個最鐘意講呢？咪政府囉，<br />\n「和平理性表達意見，社會唔亂 我地先可以對話」。<br />\n<br />\n好明顯架其實，明唔明呀？自己帶腦諗一諗啦，蠢閪。<br />\n<br />\n人地真正用緊既計 你又睇唔倒，<br />\n反而日日自己ff一堆從來唔在既計。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後又講多次，快撚d負皮我，快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要呢個post有一千負皮，<br />\n因為我好想見倒你地負皮完，勇武持續，<br />\n人權法都係過倒之後，你地扮冇嘢果個死人樣，<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我好想見倒你地真係成功吹停勇武，<br />\n之後你地後悔莫及個閪樣。<br />\n<br />\n負皮大賽開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14657523af5c474352ed86555bd3a8c2312a4a3b","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d58dce89b8bacfecdd48c67dc1966de659f4f7d","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等班蛋散叫停勇武<br />\n因就因為個人權法<br />\n仲要成班傻閪根本唔知人權法有可能十月都未過<br />\n而過左仲要可能等半年個制裁名單先出"},{"pid":"f55c41047592d41ff5991d2f961a1f97d2b82e83","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太多正皮我唔開心"},{"pid":"a7920abb241c64c78d1860b56d3da7708259647b","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"快負皮 快駁我:<br />\n<br />\n其實你話勇武要停幾多日，<br />\n但係你究竟up唔up得出人權法實際係幾時會過？<br />\n<br />\n你知咩？你肯定咩？<br />\n你唔肯定，咁你係點定勇武要停幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n十月底都未過，咁係咪等落起？<br />\n<br />\n人權法過唔過又係咪真係關勇武事？<br />\n你見唔倒蒙面法都過埋，警察開真槍急升咩？<br />\n究竟咁樣情況下去勇武反抗，<br />\n點解會影響人權法<br />\n<br />\n答唔答倒我？答唔出就收皮，<br />\n大方認你自己係on99信左d 風吹好似阿婆中寶藥黨咁"},{"pid":"1d65a059d49ad76149cbe3d9095c10afd64cc699","tid":1634413,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"啱，同外國比起上嚟根本一啲都唔暴力，到依家都未有警察死直頭係奇跡，跟返我哋一路個節奏抗爭就得，邊撚到有咁好嘢講"},{"pid":"ea5133e47aa907b910ac4d5db5d82f8e56e33019","tid":1634413,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"收爹啦豪哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VnVEAWtNwHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVnVEAWtNwHQ&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=1b085e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VnVEAWtNwHQ</a>"},{"pid":"5044261b16fd13a03070555030a4ce879b8a62a0","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d65a059d49ad76149cbe3d9095c10afd64cc699","tid":1634413,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"啱，同外國比起上嚟根本一啲都唔暴力，到依家都未有警察死直頭係奇跡，跟返我哋一路個節奏抗爭就得，邊撚到有咁好嘢講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"冇錯 我地帶節奏<br />\n我地攻佢 我地做埋文宣<br />\n最後就係佢去諗點拆<br />\n<br />\n而唔係比佢帶住<br />\n我可以好肯定講<br />\n叫停勇武呢種風同帶返慢個節奏，<br />\n想件事有機會停一停跟住降溫，<br />\n呢個正正先係對家真正既「計」。<br />\n四個月黎對家發夢都想見倒既事：<br />\n你地不如返屋企抖返一頭半個月 唔好出啦"},{"pid":"664ec9b61cf9b1f76f8d544945bee4c6460269f3","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5133e47aa907b910ac4d5db5d82f8e56e33019","tid":1634413,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"收爹啦豪哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VnVEAWtNwHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVnVEAWtNwHQ&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=1b085e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VnVEAWtNwHQ</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe104aec3a69ffce16da43d9cc1b9f64d0ecabf","tid":1634413,"uid":304363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"你係我肚入面條蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff8a27dc6250e1e6f7f06c0ca35a5c44e4f8be4","tid":1634413,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"問題係文宣開始追唔上日日都有衝突事件要解釋<br />\n連國際新聞都開始有負面<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔勇武 不過係要比時間和理非同文宣做佩合<br />\n裝修本身就好大爭議 <br />\n好多淺黃就算唔割都要消化 同 解釋 唔係佢地會覺簌失控就唔會再走來表態<br />\n<br />\n依家個問題係 把劍太前個盾跟唔上 檔唔到敵人的攻擊<br />\n<br />\n重有問題係<br />\n<br />\n好多人見到裝修文宣都唔同意 講緊係十個有六個唔支持 個結果就係要加強力度文宣解釋<br />\n<br />\n但又日日有新衝突同裝修出　文宣解唔到畫啊"},{"pid":"3b1ffaa549073c92982a570c86debf1710f4aedd","tid":1634413,"uid":280124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"上得山多終遇虎, 勇武根本唔洗日日都出, 就算出動都要有計劃而唔係亂嚟!"},{"pid":"a1a9e7f1631b66ea25ca808b94eca0c8776dbe13","tid":1634413,"uid":126062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日十月二 全民三罷 全港繼續死城 </strong></span></span><br />\n有冇人跟！！有既急需文宣！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"46ace0493cdc529f7a7674e384c6d921282800b1","tid":1634413,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:57:58.000Z","msg":"唉"}]}